Privacy Policy for Hello Dr


Introduction

Thank you for using Hello Dr. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you use our application to book doctor appointments online.

1. Information We Collect

To provide our services, we may collect and store the following types of information:

Personal Information: When you create an account or book an appointment, we may collect personal information such as your name, phone number, and email address.
Medical Information: For booking purposes, we may collect certain medical preferences or specialty requirements to help connect you with suitable doctors.
Location Information: To help match you with nearby doctors, we may collect and use location data.
Usage Data: We may collect information about how you interact with the app to improve the user experience and our services.
2. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect to:

Facilitate doctor appointments and manage your bookings.
Improve our services and user experience.
Communicate with you regarding appointments, updates, and promotions.
Ensure compliance with legal requirements.
3. Sharing Your Information

We respect your privacy and do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except:

With Medical Providers: Your booking details are shared with doctors to confirm appointments.
With Service Providers: We may use trusted third-party services to improve app functionality, including data storage and processing.
For Legal Reasons: If required by law, we may share information to comply with legal processes or protect our users and services.
4. Data Security

We take the security of your data seriously and implement industry-standard measures to protect it. However, please be aware that no security system is completely impenetrable.

5. Your Choices

You may update or delete your account information in the app settings. Please contact us if you wish to exercise your rights regarding personal data or have any concerns about our data practices.

6. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or data handling practices, please contact us at:


7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the app, and we encourage you to review the policy periodically.
